title: Not Your Normal Monday Show
description: In light of everything happening, we couldn't do a normal show.  We talk to people in the community about what's going on and change.  We talk to people that were on the 35W bridge when the semi drove into the crowd of protestors, including Jenny.  But of course sprinkle in good news and witty jabs at each other.
